6.text: Welcome to "Green Garden" Sunday Fair. All our fruit and vegetables are organic. We don't add any pesticide to grow them. Today we have special discounts for cucumber and ladies' fingers. We also have fresh baby bitter gourds. They are very good for your health. Don't forget to visit our fruit juice stall. Today's special is mixed fruit juice. Now you can buy fresh milk and yoghurt from our Dairy Corner. Enjoy your visit. Thank you.
